Class Move.AttackMove

java.lang.Object
engine.forBoard.Move
engine.forBoard.Move.AttackMove
Direct Known Subclasses:
Move.MajorAttackMove, Move.PawnAttackMove
Enclosing class:
Move
abstract static class Move.AttackMove extends Move
The AttackMove class represents a move that results in attacking an opponent's piece in chess. This abstract class provides the base functionality for all types of attack moves.
Author:
Aaron Ho
